title: A Dogwalkers Christmas Tale 2015 UPtv SDTV.x264-POKE
description:
A Dogwalker's Christmas Tale



When spoiled 21-year-old college student Luce Lockhart is forced to take a job over the holidays walking a rich developer's dog, she is surprised to find friends, four-legged and otherwise, at the local dog park. But when a new spa threatens the park, Luce must put her selfish ways to the side and work a Christmas miracle.




Original Air Date: 10-Nov-2015
